==د لیمو بدیلونه==
Many plants taste or smell similar to lemons.
* Certain cultivars of [[basil]]
* ''[[Cymbopogon]]'' (lemongrass)
* [[Lemon balm]], a mint-like herbaceous perennial in the [[Lamiaceae]] family
* Two varieties of [[Pelargonium#Scented 'geraniums'|scented geranium]]: ''Pelargonium crispum'' (lemon geranium) and ''Pelargonium x melissinum'' (lemon balm)
* [[Lemon thyme]]
* [[Lemon verbena]]
* [[Lime (fruit)|Limes]], another common sour citrus fruit, used similarly to lemons
* Certain cultivars of [[mentha|mint]]
* ''[[Magnolia grandiflora]]'' tree flowers

